              "free_text": [
                " J-25 (AID,PRANCE) neutron generator",
                "The main operational parameters of the neutron",
                "generator were the following:",
                "   * High voltage -110 KV,",
                "   * Beam curent - 100 microA,",
                "   * Beam diameter-0.5 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Square shaped (1 cm x 1 cm) high purity nickel (> 99%)",
                "and copper ( > 99.99%) foils (0.044 g and 0.0936 g,",
                "respectively) of natural isotopic abundance were",
                "prepared very precisely. The nickel and copper foils",
                "were sealed in thin polythene bags and sandwiched",
                "between three layers of aluminum flux monitor foils",
                "in the following order : (Al1 + Ni + Al2 + Cu + Al3)."
              ]
            }
